<h3>The Importance of Decentralization</h3>

<p>Decentralization is a key concept in blockchain ecosystems, referring to the ability of a network to function without a central authority or control point. In theory, this allows for more secure and transparent transactions, as there is no single point of failure that can be exploited by attackers.</p>

